data.description: Spacious and beautiful home backing up to a relaxing pond! Home features 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, fresh carpet, and a high ceilings. Open kitchen comes complete with stainless steel appliances, loads of cabinet space, and a breakfast bar. Large family room features fresh carpet and lots of built in cabinets. Huge master bedroom lead with tray ceilings leads into master bath with doubles vanities, soaking tub, and walk-in shower. The walk-in wardrobe has cabinetry with dark wood built in for all your storage needs. The expansive back porch is enclosed and is perfect for entertaining guests! Come and tour this updated home today!
